{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/craft-theme-vertical-thumbnails-and-arrows-tutorial","result":{"pageContext":{"id":1695,"date":"2022-07-04T17:00:48","date_gmt":"2022-07-04T17:00:48","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=1695"},"modified":"2022-07-04T17:45:12","modified_gmt":"2022-07-04T17:45:12","slug":"craft-theme-vertical-thumbnails-and-arrows-tutorial","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/craft-theme-vertical-thumbnails-and-arrows-tutorial/","title":{"rendered":"Craft theme: adding vertical thumbnails and arrows to the product page images"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>The Craft theme &#8211; created and made public shortly after the famous Online Store 2.0 update &#8211; is a theme inspired on the Dawn theme, but with a more refined, rustic design focused mainly (yet not exclusively) towards products that were hand crafted, as the name indicates.<br><br>Whilst being performative and attractive, the Craft theme lacks some features that would most definitely be a worthwhile add-on to its UX, such as:<br><br>&#8211; vertical thumbnails;<br>&#8211; image arrows;<br>&#8211; looping products images;<br>&#8211; dots; <br>&#8211; sync swatches when images change (and vice-versa).<br><br>Whilst these updates can be nice add-ons they do take time and effort to code, and this can shy away many merchants wanting to improve their Craft themes: lengthy back and forth emails with developers, high prices and a lack of guarantee of quality are often real deal breakers.<br><br>Therefore, today I&#8217;ll teach you how you can quickly add vertical thumbnails and much more features to your Craft theme just by pasting one piece of code, carefully and thoroughly tested by certified Shopify partners who code premium themes on a daily basis. <br><br>Plus, the best part: customizations <strong>will not be overwritten</strong>. If you have any custom code, it will still be there afterward! <br><br><a href=\"https://snippets-password-is-123.myshopify.com/products/flex-bag\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Here is a live preview of what the end result will look like.</a> (Password: <strong>123</strong>)</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-making-a-backup-of-your-theme\">Making a backup of your theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Before diving into the tutorial make sure you download the theme, so in case you face any issues you can easily revert back.<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1514\" height=\"481\" class=\"wp-image-503\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png 1514w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-600x191.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-1200x381.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-768x244.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1514px) 100vw, 1514px\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-downloading-the-files\">Downloading the files</h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/craft-theme-slider-pro\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><strong>Download </strong>the files by clicking here.</a> (<a href=\"https://snippets-password-is-123.myshopify.com/products/flex-bag\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">live preview</a>)</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-step-1-adding-the-top-code\">Step 1: adding the &#8220;top&#8221; code</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>From your Shopify admin, navigate to&nbsp;<strong>Online Store</strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Themes&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Actions&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Edit Code</strong>.<br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1349\" height=\"614\" class=\"wp-image-626\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code.jpg 1349w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code-600x273.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code-1200x546.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code-768x350.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1349px) 100vw, 1349px\" /></li><li>Type the following on the search bar:<br><br><strong>main-product.liquid</strong><br><br>And open the file that is found. <br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"872\" height=\"632\" class=\"wp-image-1562\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-1.jpg 872w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-1-850x616.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-1-768x557.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 872px) 100vw, 872px\" /></li><li>Inside the .zip you downloaded, there will be a file called <strong>top.txt</strong>. Copy all the code inside of this file.</li><li>Paste the code at the beginning of your <strong>main-product.liquid</strong> file, as the image indicates. <br><br>Before:<br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1092\" height=\"642\" class=\"wp-image-1566\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-2.jpg 1092w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-2-850x500.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-2-768x452.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1092px) 100vw, 1092px\" /><br><br>After:<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"913\" height=\"755\" class=\"wp-image-1564\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-3.jpg 913w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-3-850x703.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-3-768x635.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 913px) 100vw, 913px\" /></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3>Step 2: adding the &#8220;bottom&#8221; code</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Still inside the &#8220;main-product.liquid&#8221; file, press CTRL + F (or CMD + F on Mac) and search for:<br><br><strong>{% schema</strong><br><br>Make sure you include the space after %.<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1277\" height=\"733\" class=\"wp-image-1568\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-4.jpg 1277w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-4-850x488.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-4-1200x689.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-4-768x441.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1277px) 100vw, 1277px\" /><br></li><li>Now, delete everything <strong>below </strong>the {% schema %} line, including the {% schema %}.<strong> </strong><br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1134\" height=\"730\" class=\"wp-image-1570\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-5.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-5.jpg 1134w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-5-850x547.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-5-768x494.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1134px) 100vw, 1134px\" /></li><li>Inside the .zip you downloaded, there will be a file called <strong>bottom.txt</strong>. <br><br>Copy all the code inside of this file and paste it at the very bottom of the file.<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1364\" height=\"728\" class=\"wp-image-1572\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-6.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-6.jpg 1364w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-6-850x454.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-6-1200x640.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-6-768x410.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1364px) 100vw, 1364px\" /></li><li>That is it! </li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-final-step-activating-and-customizing-the-slider\">Final step: activating and customizing the slider</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>From your Shopify admin, navigate to&nbsp;<strong>Online Store</strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Themes&nbsp;</strong>&gt;<strong>Customize</strong>. Choose the theme that you just added the code to.<br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1699\" height=\"751\" class=\"wp-image-570\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123.jpg\" alt=\"Accessing the customize page on Shopify admin\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123.jpg 1699w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123-600x265.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123-1200x530.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123-768x339.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123-1536x679.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1699px) 100vw, 1699px\" /></li><li>At the top, from the dropdown options, select <strong>Products</strong>&gt; <strong>default product</strong>. <br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1154\" height=\"462\" class=\"wp-image-1577\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-7.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-7.jpg 1154w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-7-850x340.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-7-768x307.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1154px) 100vw, 1154px\" /></li><li>Once this page loads, click on <strong>Product Information</strong> on the left.<br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1145\" height=\"587\" class=\"wp-image-1581\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-8.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-8.jpg 1145w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-8-850x436.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-8-768x394.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1145px) 100vw, 1145px\" /></li><li>Scroll down to <strong>Media </strong>and activate whatever option you&#8217;d like. In this case, we&#8217;ll enable the vertical thumbnails:</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"381\" height=\"774\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/image-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1641\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-something-went-wrong-there-is-a-bug-or-i-can-t-install-it\">Something went wrong, there is a bug or I can&#8217;t install it</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>No worries at all! We&#8217;ll be more than happy to help you out. <br><br>Just please send us an email to <strong>ezfycode@gmail.com</strong> with your website URL and we&#8217;ll get back to you on the same day to assist you and get it installed.</p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Improve your Craft theme&#8217;s product page with performative premium code: vertical thumbnails, arrows, image loop, dots and much more.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1700,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[626],"acf":[],"image_alt":"","featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/craft_them_slider-850x478.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/craft_them_slider-200x200.png","featured_image_large_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/craft_them_slider-1200x675.png","categories_name